{"tid":2363232,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"PayPal全資持有國付寶　成內地首間全外資第三方支付機構","createTime":"2021-01-12T05:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T12:21:05.000Z","uid":185631,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a631b3b71097379146c7d7793fd8d93a3a0d6442","tid":2363232,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"美國eBay的全資子公司PayPal（美：PYPL）宣布，接手內地第三方支付平台國付寶，持股比例由70%增至100%，成了內地首家全外資的第三方支付機構。國付寶原本具國資背景，曾是海航系。<br />\n<br />\nPayPal此前已為在華擴張採取了一系列行動。去年9月，人民銀行批准PayPal收購內地支付公司國付寶的70%股份，令PayPal成為首家在華提供支付服務的外國公司。國付寶擁有互聯網支付、行動電話支付業務和跨境人民幣支付服務的許可證。<br />\n<br />\n另外，PayPal此前亦據報與銀聯合作，將允許部分銀聯卡接入PayPal網絡，銀聯用戶可將其支付卡綁定至PayPal錢包，在中國境外的地區進行電子簽帳。"},{"pid":"7b6e46d8e3aa874ca51eef3a28ea31ead44370cf","tid":2363232,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"改變到原本使用者習慣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f808451ffd4baf96a6c45b14c87fe9924939d1c","tid":2363232,"uid":212,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"中共連螞蟻都搞，會放過paypal?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0990e7937249a6852c847bf72928bf07077123c5","tid":2363232,"uid":366281,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"原本支付宝個名都幾正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家就顯得個支字好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩個可以合稱支国宝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8469b78c71820f5aa36781cfedc882ca34ea4f","tid":2363232,"uid":280593,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"比粒糖你,你就要幫佢推銀聯國際化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e13661755fad5f2ae07b95d2263214ac11d26a9","tid":2363232,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0990e7937249a6852c847bf72928bf07077123c5","t